  "title": "Temp Assistant Teacher (International School / till 23 April) *IMMEDIATE* #HAL",
  "description": "<p><strong>Working Hours: </strong></p><p>Monday - Friday 7:30am - 4:30pm.</p><p>Start asap</p><p><strong>Job Scope:</strong></p><p>● Supervise in line with the school’s behaviour and discipline policies, ensuring their welfare at all times.</p><p>● Complete observations and provide constructive feedback to teachers.</p><p>● Collaborate with class teachers to plan, deliver, and review developmentally appropriate lessons </p><p>● Assist in managing daily routines, classroom transitions, and educational activities.</p><p>● Anticipate and meet the organisational needs of the class.</p><p>● Prepare learning materials and resources, ensuring supplies are maintained.</p><p>● Work with the class teacher to create a welcoming, engaging, and well-organised learning environment.</p><p>● Support with setting up and clearing away equipment, displays, and learning materials.</p><p>● Support communication with parents, responding to queries and ensuring they receive timely information.</p><p>● Contribute to wider school activities and assist in other duties as required.</p><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><p>● A minimum of a relevant Early Childhood Care & Education (ECCE) qualification (L2/L3 or equivalent).</p><p>Interested candidate, kindly send a copy of your resume to  </p><p><strong>adelinelim@recruitexpress.com.sg</strong></p><p>Adeline Lim Xin Ying [R23112000]</p><p>Email Address: adelinelim@recruitexpress.com.sg</p><p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd</p><p>EA Licence No: 99C4599</p>",
